00:24:40,670 --> 00:24:42,870
<i>chiisana potto ni wa</i>
in the small pot

231
00:24:43,450 --> 00:24:45,270
<i>daisukina kimochi</i>
are feelings of love

232
00:24:45,530 --> 00:24:47,850
<i>yurayura to</i>
swaying softly

233
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:51,100
<i>ii kaori nosete</i>
that carry a sweet scent

234
00:24:51,760 --> 00:24:53,540
<i>itsumo matteita</i>
always waiting...

235
00:24:53,780 --> 00:25:00,340
<i>kono toki wo atatamete</i>
warming up this moment...

236
00:25:02,830 --> 00:25:07,750
<i>futari dakara wakaru koto</i>
things we understand because it's the two of us

237
00:25:08,330 --> 00:25:12,120
<i>kotoba janakute</i>
are not just words

238
00:25:13,850 --> 00:25:18,620
<i>hohoemu dake negaudake</i>
we just smile, we just hope

239
00:25:19,170 --> 00:25:23,740
<i>shizukana sora e</i>
to the quiet sky

240
00:25:24,900 --> 00:25:30,530
<i>ashita mo mata aeru yo ne</i>
we'll see each other again tomorrow...

241
00:25:32,520 --> 00:25:38,200
<i>shizukana sora de</i>
at the quiet sky

